INSERT INTO `sys_oper_log` VALUES (258, '文章管理', 2, 'com.ruoyi.cms.blog.controller.CmsBlogController.edit()', 'PUT', 1, 'admin', NULL, '/cms/blog', '127.0.0.1', '内网IP', '{\"tagIds\":[20,21,22,23,24,25,26],\"title\":\"开源分析工具在中文文献分析中的应用\",\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<div data-inline-code-theme=\\\"red\\\" data-code-block-theme=\\\"tomorrow-night\\\"><p data-lines=\\\"1\\\" data-type=\\\"p\\\" data-sign=\\\"de8f19913851b0b69b4818317bdae27c1\\\" class=\\\"cherry-highlight-line\\\">侯月明1 乔晓东1 孙 卫2 李 颖1 1 ( 中国科学技术信息研究所 北京 100038) 2 ( 中国科技出版传媒股份有限公司 北京 100717) 【摘要】对开源分析工具进行初步的调研，按照工具的开放性和可扩展性选取部分分析工具，对其技术特点和功 能进行简要介绍。综合分析工具的特点，提出基于中文文献的分析工具组合应用方案: 根据国内主要文献数据库 导出数据格式，对 SciMat 的数据导入和预处理模块进行扩展，使其能够直接处理中文文献; 利用 NWB 和 Sci2 中 集成的大量文献分析算法，对文献数据进行多角度、多层面分析; 通过 GUESS 和 VOSViewer 完成分析结果的可视 化，增加分析结果的可读性。最后，通过案例演示分析过程，验证该方案的可行性。 【关键词】中文文献 文献分析工具 文献分析 开源软件 【分类号】G35 Application of Open Source Analysis Tools in Chinese Literature Analysis Hou Yueming1 Qiao Xiaodong1 Sun Wei2 Li Ying1 1 ( Institute of Scientific ＆ Technical Information of China，Beijing 100038，China) 2 ( China Science Publishing ＆ Media LTD． ，Beijing 100717，China) 【Abstract】This paper conducts a preliminary investigation of open source analysis tools，selects part of them by openness and scalability and gives a brief introduction to their technical features and functions． After comprehensive analysis of the characteristics of the tools，this paper proposes the combined use of the tools for Chinese literature: the SciMat’s data import and pre － processing modules are expanded based on the export data formats of the main domestic literature databases， so that it can import and process the Chinese literature data directly． Integrated with a number of literature analysis algo- rithms，NWB and Sci2 are used to analyse literature from multi － scope and multi － level． The visualization of the results can increase the readability of the results，which is conducted by GUESS and VOSViewer． Finally，a case study demon- strates the analysis process and verifies the feasibility of the proposes． 【Keywords】Chinese literature Literature analysis tools Literature analysis Open source software 收稿日期: 2013 － 02 － 21 收修改稿日期: 2013 － 03 － 15 1引言 随着我国图书情', NULL, 1, '\r\n### Error updating database.  Cause: java.sql.SQLIntegrityConstraintViolationException: Duplicate entry \'22\' for key \'cms_blog_bib.PRIMARY\'\r\n### The error may exist in file [C:\\桌面\\工作\\个人\\bibview文献浏览系统\\bibview\\ruoyi-cms\\target\\classes\\mapper\\cms\\CmsBlogBibMapper.xml]\r\n### The error may involve com.ruoyi.cms.blog.mapper.CmsBlogBibMapper.insertCmsBlogBib-Inline\r\n### The error occurred while setting parameters\r\n### SQL: insert into cms_blog_bib          ( blog_id,             bib_id )           values ( ?,             ? )\r\n### Cause: java.sql.SQLIntegrityConstraintViolationException: Duplicate entry \'22\' for key \'cms_blog_bib.PRIMARY\'\n; Duplicate entry \'22\' for key \'cms_blog_bib.PRIMARY\'; nested exception is java.sql.SQLIntegrityConstraintViolationException: Duplicate entry \'22\' for key \'cms_blog_bib.PRIMARY\'', '2024-05-12 22:40:10');
